%right DEFINE LIT_LEFT INS_LEFT REGEX DEFINS DEFINED_LIST OPTCAP_LEFT TOLOWER_LEFT
TOUPPER_LEFT DEFINE_LEFT ENDTAG_LEFT LC_LEFT RC_LEFT NLC_LEFT NRC_LEFT OR_LEFT AND_LEFT
TAG_LEFT LST_LEFT SIGMA_LEFT COUNTER_LEFT
